T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Cou.Source: System behaviors may differ based on the installed country. Restart required.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Def.Source: When the extended length line is available and Preload Protocol is being used, this is the length that is selected by default.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Def.Translation: Når den forlengede linjen er tilgjengelig og Forhåndslast protokoll blir brukt, er dette lengden som blir valgt som standard.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Ext.Source: The extended length Patient Line is not available in all markets and may not be available for use with this injector.  If it is available enable this to allow Preload Protocol to work with it.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Max.Source: The system, when reducing flow to limit the pressure from exceeding the programmed pressure limit, will reduce the flow rate by a maximum of this configured value. E.g. 40% means that a programmed flow rate of 5mL/s will be reduced to no lower than 3mL/s.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Max.Translation: Når systemet reduserer strømmen for å begrense trykket fra å overstige den programmerte trykkgrensen, reduseres strømningshastigheten med maks. denne konfigurerte verdien. 40 % betyr for eksempel at en programmert strømningshastighet på 5 ml/sek. blir redusert til ikke lavere enn 3 ml/sek.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Pre.Source: High sensitivity ensures that all efforts will be taken to prevent the pressure from reaching the pressure limit, while Low sensitivity will give the system greater flexibility to maintain the programmed flow rate while still limiting pressure from greatly exceeding the pressure limit.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Pre.Translation: Høy følsomhet sikrer at alt vil bli gjort for å forhindre at trykket når trykkgrensen, mens lav følsomhet gir systemet større fleksibilitet til å opprettholde den programmerte strømningshastigheten samtidig som at trykket begrenses til å ikke overstige trykkgrensen nevneverdig.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Exam_DisableW.Source: If CENT-MWL is licensed, Hide the Patient screen and associated worklist functionality. Restart required.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Exam_DisableW.Translation: Hvis CENT-MWL er lisensiert, skjules Pasient-skjermbildet og assosiert arbeidslistefunksjon. Omstart påkrevd.

Enten var WinRE “Feilsøk, Centargo-fabrikkstandard” ikke valgt, eller det oppsto en feil.

Enten var WinRE “Feilsøk, Centargo-oppgradering” ikke valgt, eller det oppsto en feil.

Et unntak oppsto ved gjenoppretting av data etter oppgradering.

If more than one concentration is used with this protocol, convert this protocol twice -- once for each.

(If the contrast media that you use is not listed, please finish setting up the injector under Admin/Contrasts.)

Hvis mer enn én konsentrasjon brukes med denne protokollen, konverter denne protokollen to ganger -- én gang for hver.

(Hvis kontrastmediet du bruker ikke er oppgitt,  fullfør oppsett av injektoren under Admin/Kontraster.)

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Guidance.Source: If the technologist is supposed to change this protocol's volumes or flow rates based on a patient's size, then answer Yes.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Guidance.Translation: Hvis teknologen skal endre mengdene eller strømningshastighetene er basert på pasientstørrelsen, er svaret Ja.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Source: The amount of iodine given to a patient will not vary with their size.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Translation: Mengden jod som gis til en pasient varierer ikke med størrelsen deres.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Source: The amount of iodine will vary with patient size (smaller will get less and larger will get more), and the technologist will need to enter it.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Translation: Mengden jod vil variere med pasientens størrelse (mindre får mindre og større får mer) og teknologen må legge det inn.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Question.Source: Should this protocol be adjusted for patients of different sizes?
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Question.Translation: Skal denne protokollen justeres for pasienter av forskjellige størrelser?

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Guidance.Source:
Patient weight is most common, but it is also possible to use Lean Body Weight (LBW) or Body Surface Area (BSA).

LBW and BSA would have to be estimated using a published formula, and the technologist would have to enter it.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Guidance.Translation:
Pasientvekt er den vanligste, men det er også mulig å bruke mager kroppsvekt (LBW) eller kroppsoverflate (BSA).

LBW og BSA må estimeres med en publisert formel og teknologen må oppgi den.

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to calculate and enter the patient's estimated BSA.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknologen må beregne og legge inn pasientens estimerte BSA.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.ExampleContext: BSA stands for Body Surface Area

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to calculate and enter the patient's estimated LBW.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknologen må beregne og legge inn pasientens estimerte LBW.

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to either enter the patient's weight or confirm the value from the modality worklist (if available).
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknologen må enten oppgi pasientens vekt eller bekrefte verdien fra modalitetsarbeidslisten (hvis tilgjengelig).

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_Guidance.Source: If this protocol is primarily used for first-pass imaging, then it likely is for angiography.

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Translation: For organavbildning er total jodmengde nøkkelvariabelen.

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Source: For CTA, the iodine delivery rate and injection duration are the key variables.
T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Translation: For CTA er jodleveringshastigheten og injeksjonsvarigheten nøkkelvariabler.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Guidan.Source:
Usually the answer to this is No, especially for very fast scans (< 10 seconds).

If you select Yes, the technologist can change the duration of the contrast phase from the current {0} seconds to what is needed for the scan.  This means the total iodine load may go up or down, based on the duration.
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Guidan.Translation:
Vanligvis er svaret på dette Nei, spesielt for veldig raske skanninger (<10 sekunder).

Hvis du velger Ja, kan teknologen endre varigheten av kontrastfasen fra gjeldende {0} sekunder til det de trenger til skanningen.  Dette betyr at jodmengdeen kan gå opp eller ned, basert på varigheten.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Implic.Translation: Teknologen vil ikke kunne endre injeksjonens varighet.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Implic.Source: The technologist can update the injection duration based on each patient's scan duration, and the protocol will recalculate.
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Implic.Translation: Greit, teknologen kan oppdatere injeksjonens varighet basert på hver pasients skanningsvarighet og protokollen beregner på nytt.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Questi.Source: Do you need to be able to adjust the injection duration based on the scan duration?
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Questi.Translation: Trenger du å justere injeksjonens varighet basert på varigheten av skanningen?

The calculated contrast volume will never be lower than this value.

T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Questio.Source: What is the minimum amount of contrast media that should always delivered by this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q44_MinimumVolume_Questio.Translation: Hva er den minste mengden med kontrastmedium som alltid skal leveres med denne protokollen?

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Guidance.Source: Scans are either triggered using a fixed delay from the start of the contrast injection or are triggered using bolus tracking.
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Guidance.Translation: Skanninger utløses enten av en fast forsinkelse fra starten av kontrastinjeksjonen eller med bolussporing.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Source: More information is needed about how injection duration is handled when using bolus tracking.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Source: This means that the flow rate will vary per patient but the injection duration will stay constant at {0} seconds.
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Implication.Translation: Dette betyr at strømningshastigheten varierer per pasient men injeksjonens varighet holdes konstant ved {0} sekunder.

T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Question.Source: How do you handle scan timing for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q5_ScanTiming_Question.Translation: Hvordan håndterer du skanntiming for denne protokollen?

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Guidanc.Source: Fixed durations are preferred in order to keep timing as consistent as possible.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Guidanc.Translation: Fast varighet foretrekkes for å holde timingen så konsistent som mulig.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Source: This means the flow rate will be kept constant at {0} and the duration will vary based on the iodine load.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Translation: Dette betyr at strømningshastigheten vil bli holdt konstant ved {0} og at varigheten vil variere basert på jodmengden.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Source: This means that the flow rate will vary per patient but the injection duration will stay constant at {0} seconds.
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Implica.Translation: Dette betyr at strømningshastigheten varierer per pasient men injeksjonens varighet holdes konstant ved {0} sekunder.

T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Questio.Source: When using bolus tracking, a consistent injection duration is still recommended. Is it okay to use a fixed injection duration for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q51_FixedDuration_Questio.Translation: Ved bruk av bolussporing er en konsistent injeksjonsvarighet fortsatt foretrukket. Er det greit å bruke en fast injeksjonsvarighet for denne protokollen?

T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_G.Source:

T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_Q.Source: What is the highest flow rate that you would use for this protocol?
T_IodineWizard_Q52_IDL_MaximumFlowRate_Q.Translation: Hva er den høyeste strømningshastigheten du vil bruke til denne protokollen?

The calculated flow rate will never be lower than this value.

Den beregnede strømningshastigheten vil aldri være lavere enn denne verdien.

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_I.Translation: Det er ingen minimum strømningshastighet som kan øke den som er beregnet.

T_IodineWizard_Q53_IDL_MinimumFlowRate_Q.Translation: Hva er minimum strømningshastighet du synes er påkrevd for denne protokollen?

T_IodineWizardStatus_AlreadyAGenerator_D.Source: This protocol is already a Smart Protocol and does not need to be converted.

T_IodineWizardStatus_ContrastAndSalineRa.Source: This protocol has different flow rates for the contrast and saline phases and therefore cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols with constant flow rates can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_ContrastAndSalineRa.Translation: Denne protokollen har forskjellige strømningshastigheter for kontrasten og saltvannsfasene og kan derfor ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon med konstante strømningshastigheter kan konverteres nå.

T_IodineWizardStatus_DelayPhasesNotSuppo.Source: This protocol has a delay phase and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_DelayPhasesNotSuppo.Translation: Denne protokollen har en forsinkelsesfase og kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon kan konverteres nå.

T_IodineWizardStatus_DualFlowPhasesNotSu.Source: This protocol has a DualFlow phase and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol. Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_DualFlowPhasesNotSu.Translation: Denne protokollen har en DualFlow-fase og kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Dette kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll. Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon kan konverteres nå.

T_IodineWizardStatus_FirstPhaseMustBeCon.Source: The first phase of this protocol is not a contrast phase.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_FirstPhaseMustBeCon.Translation: Den første fasen av denne protokollen er ingen kontrastfase.  Dette kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon kan konverteres nå.

T_IodineWizardStatus_HasAModifier_Descri.Source: This protocol has a kVp Ruleset associated with it.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.

T_IodineWizardStatus_HasTestInjection_De.Source: This protocol has a Test Injection.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.

T_IodineWizardStatus_NoContrastsDefined_.Source: Go to Admin/Contrasts on the injector to create contrast types before attempting to convert a protocol.
T_IodineWizardStatus_NoContrastsDefined_.Translation: Gå til Admin/Kontraster på injektoren for å opprette kontrasttyper før det gjøres forsøk på å konvertere en protokoll.

T_IodineWizardStatus_ReadyToAskQuestions.Source: This protocol can be converted an equivalent iodine based protocol by answering a series of questions about how it is typically used.  When complete, the new protocol can be saved with a new name.

T_IodineWizardStatus_SecondPhaseMustBeSa.Source: The second phase of this protocol must be a saline flush phase.  This cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.

T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyInjections_D.Source: This protocol has more than one injection and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyInjections_D.Translation: Denne protokollen har mer enn én injeksjon og kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon kan konverteres nå.

T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyPhases_Descr.Source: This protocol has more than just two phases and cannot be converted to an iodine based protocol.  Only simple biphasic contrast and saline injection protocols can be converted at this time.
T_IodineWizardStatus_TooManyPhases_Descr.Translation: Denne protokollen har mer enn to faser og kan ikke konverteres til en jodbasert protokoll.  Bare enkle tofasede protokoller for kontrast- og saltvannsinjeksjon kan konverteres nå.
